contentrichtext.text: '''UFS''' may refer to: * [[Unix File System]], a file system used by many Unix and Unix-like operating systems * United Feature Syndicate, commonly known as [[United Media]] * [[University of the Free State]], a South African university * [[Universal Fighting System]], a collectible card game * United Feeder Service, a company formerly part of the [[United Express]] carrier network * [[Universal Flash Storage]] * [[Universidade Federal de Sergipe]], a [[Brazil|Brazilian]] public university based in [[São Cristóvão]], [[Sergipe]] * [[Unsupervised Forward Selection]], a data reduction algorithm * Universal Frame System, A bolt locking system standard in the construction of [[Aggressive inline skating#Frames|aggressive inline skates]] * [[United Family Services]] {{disambig}}
